<HEADLINE> Mascot of National Arts Festival Chosen </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, September 1 (Xinhua) -- The image of a smiling young
boy carrying a drum has been chosen as the emblem of China's Fifth
National Arts Festival.
</P>
<P>
Called Huanhuan, which means happiness or joy, the emblem
is the symbol of the folk culture of Sichuan province, where the
festival will be held from October 25 to Novmber 5.
</P>
<P>
