party building over the past five years.
</P>
<P>
-- The paper sings a praise for Wu Chengsheng, a commissioner
of Jingangshan -- a famed revolutionary base of late Chairman Mao
Zedong in Jiangxi province. Wu devoted his whole life to the
region's economic construction despite being scourged by cancer.
</P>
<P>
